<p>
Enterprise Sync Mode is a global strategy toggle in Settings that enables
enterprise-style sync behavior across the app. When this preference is turned
on, ABM Warranty applies a consistent job execution model intended for larger
tenant environments and more structured operational flows.
</p>

<p>
This section is a placeholder and will be expanded with full implementation
